hep.aida
Interface IPlotterStyle

All Superinterfaces:
IBaseStyle
public interface IPlotterStyle
extends IBaseStyle

User level interface to plotter style. A plotter style permit to customize various part of the plotting "scene" (axes, titles, data representations, etc...)

Author:
The AIDA team (http://aida.freehep.org/)
